title: Poser - Irina SP3 reload
description:
This is my first upload, so it is more of a test than anything. This is the best Daz3D Stephanie 3.0 morph that I believe was created, Blackhearted Irina 2.0 on Renderosity. Its a collection of the most basic things for the character, read list below.

BlackEyes 2.0 = based on real human eye geometry, these high-resolution smart-props replace the Millennium default eyes 

Irina 2.0 = perfectly defined muscles and skin detail, not to mention an amazingly realistic and sexy body shape

Irina Adventuress = set of realistic clothing and gear that gives Irina a sexy, yet functional outfit for her adventuring needs

Stephanie 3.0 Petite Base SR1 = includes all new technology introduced with Victoria 3, in a spunky, sassy, petite package

Tara = custom head morph & textures that adds more versatility to the Irina pack

3 short hair add-on = Clandestine, Erin and SMS Hair

3 long hair add-on = Rose Curls, Slick and Starlet Hair
